    <text id="B0350T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>DeLamater confirms the admission of two black women to Howard's Grove Hospital in
                    Richmond for treatment for insanity.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees">R.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Freedmen">F.</abbr> and <abbr expan="Abandoned">A.</abbr>
                    Lands<lb/>Office <abbr expan="Surgeon">Surg.</abbr> in <abbr expan="Chief">Chf.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="District of Virginia">Dist. Va.</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient">Mr. Thomas Jackson<lb/>Agent Bureau <abbr
                            expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R.F. and
                        A.L.</abbr><lb/>Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-10-21"><abbr expan="October">Oct.</abbr> 21st 1867</date>
                        <name type="place">Richmond <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir:</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I forward to you enclosed an order to <abbr expan="Assistant Adjutant Surgeon"
                        >A.A. Surg.</abbr>
                    <hi rend="underline">D.R. Brown</hi>
                    <abbr expan="United States Army">U.S.A.</abbr> to receive in the ward for the
                    insane at Howard Grove Hospital Richmond <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr> for
                    treatment and security of <hi rend="underline">Louisa J. Williams</hi> and <hi
                        rend="underline">Lucy Paine</hi> indigent insane colored persons, the order
                    being made at your request, with the understanding that the civil authorities
                    furnish the necessary transportation.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am respectfully yours &amp;c</salute>
                    <signed>J. J. DeLamater<lb/><abbr expan="Brevet Lieutenant Colonel">Bvt. Lieut.
                            Col</abbr> and <abbr expan="Surgeon">Surg.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="United States Army">USA</abbr><lb/><abbr
                            expan="Surgeon in Chief">Surg in chf</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="District">Dist</abbr> of <abbr expan="Virginia"
                        >Va</abbr><lb/>Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees">R.</abbr><abbr expan="Freedmen"
                            >F.</abbr> and <abbr expan="Abandoned">A.</abbr> Lands</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
